The '''Nothoiin Corridor''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace route]] forged by [[Ecclessis Figg/Legends|Ecclessis Figg]], going from [[Gerrenthum/Legends|Gerrenthum]] on the [[Corellian Trade Spine/Legends|Corellian Trade Spine]], through the [[Ivax Nebula/Legends|Ivax Nebula]] to [[Nothoiin/Legends|Nothoiin]], and finally to the old [[Eriadu Way]] segment of the [[Hydian Way/Legends|Hydian Way]].<ref name="GG" />

